# Settings Screen Specification

- **Header:** Avatar, name, role badge, quick link to preview public profile.
- **Section Cards:** Profile, Payments, Notifications, Integrations, Security each with icon and description.
- **Detail View:** Expands in modal sheet (mobile) or right panel (tablet) with form fields grouped logically.
- **Support CTA:** Persistent footer link to help centre and live chat.
- **Audit Banner:** Displays last update timestamp and compliance reminders.
